title: Episode 5 - What’s Your Magic Number
itunes:title: Episode 5 - What’s Your Magic Number
description:
The Doughertys have managed to elude law enforcement as they’ve crossed over state lines from Florida into Georgia. Realizing they’ll need to fund their get away to Mexico, the siblings make a choice that will take their situation in the eyes of the law, from bad to worse… they decide to rob a bank.
